The People of the State of New York, Respondent, v Christopher B., Appellant.

Judgment, Supreme Court, Bronx County, rendered on August 10,1979, unanimously affirmed. The order of this court entered on October 30, 1980 is vacated. No opinion. Concur — Kupferman, J. P., Sandler, Markewich, Bloom and Yesawich, JJ.
